2022-05-17T16:12:35Z	How to upgrade yarn.social running as a [vultr app](https://www.vultr.com/marketplace/apps/yarn):  - download the latest binary from https://git.mills.io/yarnsocial/yarn/releases - `systemctl stop yarnd.service ` - `cd /usr/bin/local` - `cp yarnd yarnd_old` - upload yarnd to /usr/bin/local - `chmod +x yarnd` - `reboot`  Enjoy!
